{"tid":532562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港應該鼓勵多d蝻玩parkour","createTime":"2018-01-18T03:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T03:19:38.000Z","uid":136455,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6f4e920b376e7a9839f1183a6f69825760d4f7","tid":532562,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9d476F9Kip4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9d476F9Kip4&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=871a8dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9d476F9Kip4</a><br />\n【本報訊】一名身穿校服的印度裔少年，昨晚在油麻地文華樓19樓天台嬉戲，現場消息稱，該少年（圖）疑一時興起，效法極限運動Parkour飛躍道，在天台邊緣跳躍，豈料失足墮樓，幸撞及多個冷氣機及冷氣槽卸去下墜力，不致當場喪命，同學大驚報警，男生事被送院搶救，目前情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e993c2e684cfe1f3de7cfedb50b85881702dbc","tid":532562,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d93561f36feb3550c14d96a7b614e9695d7c09","tid":532562,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9d476F9Kip4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9d476F9Kip4&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=871a8dc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9d476F9Kip4</a>"},{"pid":"3cee7ae1b80a99894ba0f7d52149b18bd4dd30a4","tid":532562,"uid":28695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"卸去下墜力是一個不幸"},{"pid":"d006fba87d8f30e3abd76cf0a0c309e92b36a03f","tid":532562,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"壓到人點算<br />\n花花草草仲緊要